        "data": {
          "comment": "# 🎞️ Crossfade Montage\n\nStitch two clips with a crossfade and lay a music bed over the top — a complete edit, no AI.\n\n**Pipeline:** Clip A + Clip B → transition (fade) → add music → output.\n\n**Try this:** swap `transition_type` (wipeleft, circleopen, dissolve…), tune `duration`, and set `mix` on Add Audio to keep the original clip sound under the music."
        },
